author: Sara Schonhardt
title: Indonesia’s Joko Widodo to Talk Tech on U.S. Trip
text:
JAKARTA, Indonesia—Indonesian President Joko Widodo will meet some of the leading U.S. venture-capital and technology companies next week, during a stop in Silicon Valley aimed at drumming up investment and interest in Southeast Asia’s largest economy.
